data.description: Discover the countless upgrades in this immaculate East Medford residence! Nestled on a private flag lot, you'll find ample parking. Step inside to experience a warm and inviting color palette that unifies the open floor plan, featuring new laminate flooring, fresh paint, and updated stone accents on the cozy wood-burning fireplace. The fully remodeled kitchen is a showstopper, a sleek tile backsplash stretching to the ceiling, butcher block countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Plus, there's room for negotiation on a built-in fridge. The spacious primary bedroom is accompanied by a fully renovated en-suite bath with a walk-in shower and a vanity area. The guest rooms are generously sized and share a remodeled guest bath, and you'll appreciate the roomy laundry area with ample storage. Outside, the property boasts a good-sized fenced backyard, a charming, shaded patio, and an elevated deck, perfect for hosting. Schedule a showing today!
